COLIN QUINN: I would like
to do more cop shows,

00:35:02.554 --> 00:35:03.790
now that you mentioned it.

00:35:03.790 --> 00:35:05.980
That's really my-- do
you know what I mean?

00:35:05.980 --> 00:35:08.650
In fact, now that I'm here at
