DAVID WINDMUELLER: Playing until
March 16 at the Minetta Lane

00:43:25.550 --> 00:43:26.420
Theater.

00:43:26.420 --> 00:43:28.100
And we thank you
very much for coming.

00:43:28.100 --> 00:43:29.391
COLIN QUINN: Thank you so much.

00:43:29.391 --> 00:43:30.140
Thank you guys.

00:43:30.140 --> 00:43:31.990
Thank you.

